platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Prepare delicious meals and maximize your grocery trips with this beautifully designed cooking app. Epicurious hosts thousands of searchable recipes across a wide range of categories, and you can easily save them to an organized recipe box or generate handy shopping lists. The more we use Epicurious, the more we love its timely content, mouthwatering photos, helpful customer ratings, and overall presentation.
